PHASE 3 PLACEHOLDER

This file represents the Stage 4 interaction specification artifacts that will be
shipped in Phase 3. In production, Stage 4 produces:
- Mermaid stateDiagram-v2 files (canonical designer-readable artifact)
- XState v5 machine files (for components with async + ≥3 states + conditional transitions)
- IxD spec Markdown files validated against interaction-spec.v1.json

State machines planned for Stage 4 → 5 handoff:
- SearchBox: idle → searching → results → empty-state / error-state
- ContextPanel: collapsed → expanded → loading → loaded / error
- KnowledgeBaseEntry: view → edit → saving → saved / conflict

